_sText: -A proper good night-time map if I may say so myself :) -16 spawns for each team, total of 32 -Reccomended size: 8-32 players (the more the better really) -2 CT spawns in each tower -Bomb sites are the two downstairs rooms on either side of the warehouse -Working elevator (left button is down, right button is up) -Door sounds for the big heavy ones. -Fairly extensive nav-meshing. -Place-names [radio locations] (not on the radar though, I would do it, but I don't have the software) -Oh, and did I mention it's at night? (sorry, I really love nightfights) Please do not share or edit this map without my permission Ask via my FSPB account if you would like to make any changes or share this map If I give permission for you to do so, then please would you put my name in the credits, after all, it is my map Thanks :) Oh and one more thing... If any servers are running this map, could you let me know? I'd love to play it online against real people :)
